Average Values

Input: a collection of (structured) textual csv files containing the daily value of PM10 for a set of sensors
    ▪Each line of the files has the following format: sensorId,date,PM10 value (μg/m3 )

Output: compute the average PM10 value
    ▪Print the result on the standard output



i.e.
s1,2016-01-01,20.5
s2,2016-01-01,30.1
s1,2016-01-02,60.2
s2,2016-01-02,20.4
s1,2016-01-03,55.5
s2,2016-01-03,52.5

----

39.86